      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"rest\" sounds almost... comforting. Like the noise finally just stops. Everything is so loud and exhausting all the time. If I just stayed still and let the journey finish, would it really be that bad? To just stop trying to find the next thing?",
